{{ header }}
<style>
  .my-download{
    color: rgb(54,167,218);
    text-decoration: underline;
    vertical-align: bottom;
    text-transform:none !important;
  }
  .my-tip-title{
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .sub-title{
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
  .mrb5{
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }
</style>

<script src="catalog/view/javascript/layer/layer.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="catalog/view/javascript/bootstrap/js/bootstrap-paginator.min.js"></script>


<div id="page-bid-list-spot-price-bid" class="page-seller-portal">
  {#菜单#}
  {% include 'giga/template/_parts/breadcrumb_simple.twig' %}
  {#END 菜单#}

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1>Import Item Code Mapping Guide</h1>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <p class="my-tip-title">Step 1</p>
            <p>Click ‘
              <a href="{{itemCodeMappingTemplate}}" download="Download Template" class="my-download">
                Download Template
              </a>’ to download the template for file import</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="my-tip-title">Step 2</p>
            <p>Enter the value of ‘Platform,’ ‘Platform SKU,’ and ‘B2B Item Code.’</p>
            <p class="sub-title">Please notice:</p>
            <p class="mrb5">1. Platform refers to the external sales platform. Please only enter
              {% if country_id == 223 %}
                Amazon / Wayfair / Walmart / eBay.
              {% elseif country_id == 81 %}
                Wayfair.
              {% elseif country_id == 222 %}
                Amazon / Wayfair.
              {% else %}

              {% endif %}
              We currently don’t accept entering other sales platforms.</p>
            <p class="mrb5">2. Platform SKU refers to the product SKU on a specific sales platform. For example, B2B Item Code refers to the corresponding product Item Code on B2B Platform to Platform SKU.</p>
            <p class="mrb5">3. Each SKU on each sales platform can only correspond to one B2B Platform Item Code.</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="my-tip-title">Step 3</p>
            <p>Click ‘IMPORT’ on the listing page, select the prepared file, and import. The file has failed to be imported if it notifies you with an error message. Please modify the file and import it again. The file is successfully imported if it notifies ‘Imported successfully.’</p>
            <hr>
            <hr>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
{{ footer }}